About the weak alias, you would add to `logging.h`:

```
extern void log(u8 level, const char *msg) __attribute__ ((weak, alias ("_log_default")));
```

and in `logging.c`:
```
const char *level_string[] = {"DEBUG", "INFO", "WARNING", "ERROR"};
void _log_default(u8 level, const char *msg)
{
    printf("%s: %s", level_string[level], msg);
}
```

